#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/income_tax_calculator.html:519
msgid "What is the standard deduction for 2024?"
msgstr "Qual è la detrazione standard per il 2024?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/income_tax_calculator.html:520
msgid ""
"For 2024, the standard deduction is $14,600 for single filers, $29,200 for "
"married filing jointly, and $21,900 for head of household."
msgstr ""
"Per il 2024, la detrazione standard è di $ 14.600 per i dichiaranti single, "
"$ 29.200 per i dichiaranti coniugati congiuntamente e $ 21.900 per il "
"capofamiglia."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/income_tax_calculator.html:524
#, python-format
msgid ""
"FICA includes Social Security tax (6.2%% on income up to $168,600) and "
"Medicare tax (1.45%% on all income, plus 0.9%% on income over $200,000 for "
"single filers)."
msgstr ""
"La FICA comprende l'imposta sulla previdenza sociale (6,2%% sul reddito fino"
" a $ 168.600) e l'imposta Medicare (1,45%% su tutto il reddito, più 0,9%% "
"sul reddito superiore a $ 200.000 per coloro che presentano una domanda "
"unica)."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/income_tax_calculator.html:527
msgid "Should I itemize or take the standard deduction?"
msgstr "Devo dettagliare o prendere la detrazione standard?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/income_tax_calculator.html:528
msgid ""
"Itemize only if your total itemized deductions exceed the standard "
"deduction. Common itemized deductions include mortgage interest, state/local"
" taxes (up to $10,000), and charitable contributions."
msgstr ""
"Dettaglia solo se le detrazioni dettagliate totali superano la detrazione "
"standard. Le detrazioni dettagliate più comuni includono interessi "
"ipotecari, tasse statali/locali (fino a $ 10.000) e contributi di "
"beneficenza."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/income_tax_calculator.html:531
msgid "How can I reduce my taxable income?"
msgstr "Come posso ridurre il mio reddito imponibile?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/income_tax_calculator.html:532
msgid ""
"Contribute to pre-tax accounts like 401(k), traditional IRA, or HSA. These "
"reduce your AGI and therefore your taxable income."
msgstr ""
"Contribuisci a conti al lordo delle imposte come 401 (k), IRA tradizionale o"
" HSA. Questi riducono la tua AGI e quindi il tuo reddito imponibile."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/income_tax_calculator.html:543
