msgstr "Visualizza i tuoi risultati"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:346
msgid "See your projected savings growth with detailed charts and breakdowns."
msgstr ""
"Visualizza la crescita dei tuoi risparmi prevista con grafici dettagliati e "
"suddivisioni."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:354
msgid "Savings Strategies"
msgstr "Strategie di risparmio"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:357
msgid "Pay Yourself First"
msgstr "Prima paga te stesso"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:358
msgid ""
"Set up automatic transfers to your savings account on payday. This ensures "
"you save before spending on discretionary items."
msgstr ""
"Imposta i trasferimenti automatici sul tuo conto di risparmio il giorno "
"dello stipendio. Ciò ti garantisce di risparmiare prima di spendere in "
"articoli discrezionali."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:360
msgid "The 50/30/20 Rule"
msgstr "La regola del 50/30/20"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:361
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Allocate 50%% of income to needs, 30%% to wants, and 20%% to savings. This "
"simple framework helps maintain balance."
msgstr ""
"Destinare il 50%% del reddito ai bisogni, il 30%% ai desideri e il 20%% ai "
"risparmi. Questa semplice struttura aiuta a mantenere l’equilibrio."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:364
msgid "High-Yield Savings Accounts"
msgstr "Conti di risparmio ad alto rendimento"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:365
msgid ""
"Online banks often offer higher interest rates than traditional banks. Even "
"small differences add up over time."
msgstr ""
"Le banche online offrono spesso tassi di interesse più elevati rispetto alle"
" banche tradizionali. Anche le piccole differenze si sommano nel tempo."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:367
msgid "Emergency Fund First"
msgstr "Innanzitutto il Fondo di Emergenza"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:368
msgid ""
"Before investing, build an emergency fund covering 3-6 months of expenses. "
"This provides financial security."
msgstr ""
"Prima di investire, crea un fondo di emergenza che copra 3-6 mesi di spese. "
"Ciò fornisce sicurezza finanziaria."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:385
#, python-format
msgid ""
"A common guideline is to save at least 20%% of your income. However, the "
"right amount depends on your goals, expenses, and timeline. Use the 'Monthly"
" deposit needed' calculation to find the exact amount for your specific "
"goal."
msgstr ""
"Una linea guida comune è quella di risparmiare almeno il 20%% del tuo "
"reddito. Tuttavia, l’importo giusto dipende dai tuoi obiettivi, dalle spese "
"e dalla tempistica. Utilizza il calcolo del \"Deposito mensile necessario\" "
"per trovare l'importo esatto per il tuo obiettivo specifico."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:391
msgid "What's a good interest rate for savings?"
msgstr "Qual è un buon tasso di interesse per il risparmio?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:397
#, python-format
msgid ""
"High-yield savings accounts currently offer 4-5%% APY. Traditional banks may"
" offer less than 0.5%%. Shop around for the best rates, and consider online "
"banks which typically offer higher rates."
msgstr ""
"I conti di risparmio ad alto rendimento offrono attualmente il 4-5% di APY. "
"Le banche tradizionali possono offrire meno dello 0,5%%. Cerca le tariffe "
"migliori e prendi in considerazione le banche online che in genere offrono "
"tariffe più elevate."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:403
msgid "What's the difference between APY and interest rate?"
msgstr "Qual è la differenza tra APY e tasso di interesse?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:409
msgid ""
"APY (Annual Percentage Yield) includes the effect of compounding, showing "
"your actual annual return. The interest rate (APR) doesn't include "
"compounding. APY gives you a more accurate picture of your earnings."
msgstr ""
"L'APY (rendimento percentuale annuale) include l'effetto della "
"capitalizzazione, mostrando il rendimento annuale effettivo. Il tasso di "
"interesse (APR) non include la capitalizzazione. APY ti offre un quadro più "
"accurato dei tuoi guadagni."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:415
msgid "Should I save or invest?"
msgstr "Dovrei risparmiare o investire?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:421
msgid ""
"Use savings for short-term goals (1-3 years) and emergency funds. For long-"
"term goals (5+ years), consider investing in stocks or index funds which "
"historically provide higher returns despite more volatility."
msgstr ""
"Utilizzare i risparmi per obiettivi a breve termine (1-3 anni) e fondi di "
"emergenza. Per obiettivi a lungo termine (oltre 5 anni), valuta la "
"possibilità di investire in azioni o fondi indicizzati che storicamente "
"forniscono rendimenti più elevati nonostante una maggiore volatilità."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:435
msgid "Automate your savings - set up automatic transfers on payday."
msgstr ""
"Automatizza i tuoi risparmi: imposta i trasferimenti automatici il giorno di"
" paga."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:441
msgid "Save windfalls - put bonuses, tax refunds, and gifts into savings."
msgstr ""
"Risparmia guadagni inaspettati: metti bonus, rimborsi fiscali e regali nel "
"risparmio."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:447
msgid "Track your spending to find areas where you can cut back."
msgstr ""
"Tieni traccia delle tue spese per trovare le aree in cui puoi tagliare."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:453
msgid "Set specific goals - you're more likely to save with a clear target."
msgstr ""
"Stabilisci obiettivi specifici: avrai maggiori probabilità di risparmiare "
"con un obiettivo chiaro."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:581
msgid "Time to Goal"
msgstr "È ora di raggiungere l'obiettivo"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:588
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:197
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/date_calculator.html:98
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_counter.html:96
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_the_week_calculator.html:155
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_the_week_calculator.html:185
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_week_calculator.html:155
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_week_calculator.html:185
msgid "End Date"
msgstr "Data di fine"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:597
msgid "You will reach your goal with"
msgstr "Raggiungerai il tuo obiettivo con"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:597
msgid "extra!"
msgstr "extra!"

