#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:18
msgid "Calculate student loan payments and compare repayment plans."
msgstr ""
"Calcola le rate del prestito studentesco e confronta i piani di rimborso."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:56
msgid ""
"Calculate your monthly student loan payment, compare repayment plans, and "
"see how extra payments can help you become debt-free faster."
msgstr ""
"Calcola la rata mensile del prestito studentesco, confronta i piani di "
"rimborso e scopri come i pagamenti extra possono aiutarti a liberarti dai "
"debiti più velocemente."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:72
msgid "Total Loan Amount"
msgstr "Importo totale del prestito"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:90
#, python-format
msgid "Federal loans: 5-7%%, Private: varies"
msgstr "Prestiti federali: 5-7%, privati: varia"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:95
msgid "Repayment Term"
msgstr "Termine di rimborso"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:102
msgid "Extended"
msgstr "Esteso"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:117
msgid "See how extra payments save you money"
msgstr "Scopri come i pagamenti extra ti fanno risparmiare denaro"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:164
msgid "Save"
msgstr "Salva"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:165
msgid "years earlier!"
msgstr "anni prima!"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:189
msgid "Compare Repayment Plans"
msgstr "Confronta i piani di rimborso"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:194
msgid "Plan"
msgstr "Piano"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:259
msgid "Plan Your Student Loan Payoff"
msgstr "Pianifica il rimborso del tuo prestito studentesco"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:260
msgid ""
"Enter your loan details to see payment options and how to pay off your loans"
" faster."
msgstr ""
"Inserisci i dettagli del tuo prestito per visualizzare le opzioni di "
"pagamento e come ripagare i tuoi prestiti più velocemente."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:274
msgid ""
"Input your total loan balance and interest rate from your loan servicer."
msgstr ""
"Inserisci il saldo totale del prestito e il tasso di interesse dal tuo "
"gestore di prestiti."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:280
msgid "Choose Term"
msgstr "Scegli Termine"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:281
msgid ""
"Select your repayment term - shorter terms mean higher payments but less "
"interest."
msgstr ""
"Seleziona la durata del rimborso: termini più brevi significano pagamenti "
"più elevati ma meno interessi."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:287
msgid "Compare Plans"
msgstr "Confronta i piani"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:288
msgid ""
"See how different plans and extra payments affect your payoff timeline."
msgstr ""
"Scopri come i diversi piani e i pagamenti extra influiscono sulla cronologia"
" dei tuoi guadagni."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:300
msgid "What repayment plan should I choose?"
msgstr "Quale piano di rimborso devo scegliere?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:306
msgid ""
"Standard 10-year is best if you can afford it - you'll pay the least "
"interest. If payments are too high, consider income-driven plans or extended"
" repayment. Always pay as much as you can afford."
msgstr ""
"Il contratto standard a 10 anni è il migliore se te lo puoi permettere: "
"pagherai il minor interesse. Se i pagamenti sono troppo alti, prendi in "
"considerazione piani orientati al reddito o un rimborso prolungato. Paga "
"sempre quanto puoi permetterti."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:318
msgid ""
"Extra payments go directly to principal, reducing the balance faster. This "
"means less interest over time and earlier payoff. Even $50/month extra can "
"save thousands and years on your loan."
msgstr ""
"I pagamenti extra vanno direttamente al capitale, riducendo il saldo più "
"velocemente. Ciò significa meno interessi nel tempo e un ritorno anticipato."
" Anche $ 50 al mese in più possono farti risparmiare migliaia e anni sul tuo"
" prestito."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:324
msgid "What about loan forgiveness?"
msgstr "E la remissione del prestito?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:330
msgid ""
"Public Service Loan Forgiveness (PSLF) forgives remaining balance after 120 "
"qualifying payments while working for government/nonprofit. Income-driven "
"plans forgive after 20-25 years. Forgiven amounts may be taxable."
msgstr ""
"Il condono del prestito di servizio pubblico (PSLF) condona il saldo "
"rimanente dopo 120 pagamenti qualificanti mentre si lavora per il "
"governo/non-profit. I piani basati sul reddito perdonano dopo 20-25 anni. "
"Gli importi condonati possono essere imponibili."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:336
msgid "Should I refinance my student loans?"
msgstr "Dovrei rifinanziare i miei prestiti studenteschi?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:342
msgid ""
"Refinancing can lower your rate if you have good credit and stable income. "
"However, refinancing federal loans means losing benefits like income-driven "
"plans and forgiveness options. Only refinance if you don't need these "
"protections."
msgstr ""
"Il rifinanziamento può abbassare il tasso se disponi di un buon credito e di"
" un reddito stabile. Tuttavia, rifinanziare i prestiti federali significa "
"perdere benefici come piani orientati al reddito e opzioni di condono. "
"Rifinanzia solo se non hai bisogno di queste protezioni."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:350
msgid "Student Loan Tips"
msgstr "Suggerimenti per il prestito agli studenti"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:356
#, python-format
msgid "Set up autopay - most servicers offer a 0.25%% rate reduction."
msgstr ""
"Imposta il pagamento automatico: la maggior parte dei servizi offre una "
"riduzione della tariffa dello 0,25%."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:362
msgid ""
"Pay highest interest loans first (avalanche method) to minimize interest."
msgstr ""
"Pagare prima i prestiti con gli interessi più alti (metodo a valanga) per "
"ridurre al minimo gli interessi."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:368
msgid ""
"Make payments during grace period to reduce principal before interest "
"accrues."
msgstr ""
"Effettuare pagamenti durante il periodo di grazia per ridurre il capitale "
"prima che maturino gli interessi."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:374
msgid ""
"Check for employer student loan assistance - it's an increasingly common "
"benefit."
msgstr ""
"Controlla l'assistenza per il prestito studentesco da parte del datore di "
"lavoro: è un vantaggio sempre più comune."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/take_home_paycheck_calculator.html:5
msgid "Take Home Paycheck Calculator - Calculate Net Pay"
msgstr ""
"Calcolatore dello stipendio da portare a casa: calcola la retribuzione netta"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/take_home_paycheck_calculator.html:7
msgid ""
"Calculate your take-home pay after federal taxes, state taxes, Social "
"Security, Medicare, and deductions. See your net paycheck breakdown."
msgstr ""
"Calcola la tua paga da portare a casa dopo le tasse federali, le tasse "
"statali, la previdenza sociale, l'assistenza sanitaria statale e le "
"detrazioni. Visualizza la ripartizione della tua busta paga netta."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/take_home_paycheck_calculator.html:10
