msgstr "Standard di grasso corporeo dell'esercito americano"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:5
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:27
msgid ""
"Calculate body fat percentage using US Army measurement standards. Check if "
"you meet Army body fat requirements."
msgstr ""
"Calcola la percentuale di grasso corporeo utilizzando gli standard di "
"misurazione dell'esercito americano. Controlla se soddisfi i requisiti di "
"grasso corporeo dell'esercito."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:41
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:73
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_surface_area_calculator.html:73
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:73
