#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:366
msgid "What is Basal Metabolic Rate (BMR)?"
msgstr "Cos'è il tasso metabolico basale (BMR)?"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:368
msgid ""
"Basal Metabolic Rate (BMR) is the number of calories your body needs to "
"perform basic life-sustaining functions while at complete rest. These "
"functions include breathing, circulation, cell production, brain and nerve "
"function, and maintaining body temperature."
msgstr ""
"Il tasso metabolico basale (BMR) è il numero di calorie di cui il tuo corpo "
"ha bisogno per svolgere le funzioni di sostegno vitale di base mentre è a "
"riposo completo. Queste funzioni includono la respirazione, la circolazione,"
" la produzione cellulare, la funzione cerebrale e nervosa e il mantenimento "
"della temperatura corporea."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:371
#, python-format
msgid ""
"BMR accounts for approximately 60-75%% of your total daily calorie "
"expenditure. It's the minimum number of calories you need to consume daily "
"to maintain basic bodily functions."
msgstr ""
"Il BMR rappresenta circa il 60-75%% del dispendio calorico giornaliero "
"totale. È il numero minimo di calorie che devi consumare quotidianamente per"
" mantenere le funzioni corporee di base."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:377
msgid "What is Total Daily Energy Expenditure (TDEE)?"
msgstr "Cos’è la spesa energetica giornaliera totale (TDEE)?"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:379
msgid ""
"Total Daily Energy Expenditure (TDEE) is your total daily calorie burn, "
"including BMR plus calories burned through physical activity, exercise, and "
"the thermic effect of food (calories burned digesting food)."
msgstr ""
"La spesa energetica giornaliera totale (TDEE) è il consumo calorico "
"giornaliero totale, compreso il BMR più le calorie bruciate attraverso "
"l'attività fisica, l'esercizio e l'effetto termico del cibo (calorie "
"bruciate durante la digestione del cibo)."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:382
msgid ""
"TDEE = BMR × Activity Multiplier. This represents the total number of "
"calories you burn in a day, which is crucial for weight management."
msgstr ""
"TDEE = BMR × Moltiplicatore di attività. Questo rappresenta il numero totale"
" di calorie bruciate in un giorno, che è fondamentale per la gestione del "
"peso."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:388
msgid "BMR Calculation Formulas"
msgstr "Formule di calcolo del BMR"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:391
msgid "Mifflin-St Jeor Equation (Recommended)"
msgstr "Equazione di Mifflin-St Jeor (consigliata)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:393
msgid "Most accurate for modern populations. Considered the gold standard."
msgstr ""
"Più accurato per le popolazioni moderne. Considerato il gold standard."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:396
msgid "Men: BMR = 10 × weight(kg) + 6.25 × height(cm) - 5 × age(years) + 5"
msgstr "Uomini: BMR = 10 × peso(kg) + 6,25 × altezza(cm) - 5 × età(anni) + 5"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:397
msgid ""
"Women: BMR = 10 × weight(kg) + 6.25 × height(cm) - 5 × age(years) - 161"
msgstr ""
"Donne: BMR = 10 × peso (kg) + 6,25 × altezza (cm) - 5 × età (anni) - 161"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:401
msgid "Harris-Benedict Equation (Revised)"
msgstr "Equazione di Harris-Benedict (rivista)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:403
msgid ""
"Older formula, still widely used. May overestimate BMR for some individuals."
msgstr ""
"Formula più vecchia, ancora ampiamente utilizzata. Può sovrastimare il BMR "
"per alcuni individui."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:406
msgid ""
"Men: BMR = 13.397 × weight(kg) + 4.799 × height(cm) - 5.677 × age(years) + "
"88.362"
msgstr ""
"Uomini: BMR = 13.397 × peso(kg) + 4.799 × altezza(cm) - 5.677 × età(anni) + "
"88.362"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:407
msgid ""
"Women: BMR = 9.247 × weight(kg) + 3.098 × height(cm) - 4.330 × age(years) + "
"447.593"
msgstr ""
"Donne: BMR = 9.247 × peso(kg) + 3.098 × altezza(cm) - 4.330 × età(anni) + "
"447.593"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:411
msgid "Katch-McArdle Formula"
msgstr "Formula di Katch-McArdle"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:413
msgid ""
"Most accurate when body fat percentage is known. Uses lean body mass instead"
" of total weight."
msgstr ""
"Più accurato quando è nota la percentuale di grasso corporeo. Utilizza la "
"massa corporea magra invece del peso totale."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:416
msgid "BMR = 370 + (21.6 × Lean Body Mass in kg)"
msgstr "BMR = 370 + (21,6 × Massa corporea magra in kg)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:419
msgid ""
"Note: This calculator estimates lean body mass based on gender averages."
msgstr ""
"Nota: questo calcolatore stima la massa corporea magra in base alle medie di"
" genere."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:427
msgid "Activity Level Multipliers"
msgstr "Moltiplicatori del livello di attività"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:429
msgid "Little or no exercise, desk job"
msgstr "Poco o nessun esercizio fisico, lavoro d'ufficio"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:430
msgid "Light exercise 1-3 days per week"
msgstr "Esercizio leggero 1-3 giorni a settimana"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:431
msgid "Moderate exercise 3-5 days per week"
msgstr "Esercizio moderato 3-5 giorni a settimana"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:432
msgid "Hard exercise 6-7 days per week"
msgstr "Esercizio intenso 6-7 giorni a settimana"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:433
msgid "Very hard exercise, physical job"
msgstr "Esercizio molto duro, lavoro fisico"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:434
msgid "Professional athlete, extremely active"
msgstr "Atleta professionista, estremamente attiva"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:443
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:474
msgid "Enter your gender, age, height, and weight"
msgstr "Inserisci il tuo sesso, età, altezza e peso"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:444
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:475
msgid "Select your activity level based on your weekly exercise routine"
msgstr ""
"Seleziona il tuo livello di attività in base alla tua routine di allenamento"
" settimanale"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:445
msgid "Click 'Calculate BMR' to see your results"
msgstr "Fai clic su \"Calcola BMR\" per visualizzare i risultati"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:446
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:456
msgid "Review your BMR, TDEE, calorie targets, and macro recommendations"
msgstr "Controlla il tuo BMR, TDEE, obiettivi calorici e consigli macro"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:447
msgid "Use the calorie targets to plan your diet based on your goals"
msgstr ""
"Utilizza gli obiettivi calorici per pianificare la tua dieta in base ai tuoi"
" obiettivi"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:456
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:410
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:465
msgid "BMR (Basal Metabolic Rate)"
msgstr "BMR (tasso metabolico basale)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:458
msgid ""
"The number of calories your body burns at rest. This is your baseline "
"calorie requirement for basic bodily functions."
msgstr ""
"Il numero di calorie che il tuo corpo brucia a riposo. Questo è il "
"fabbisogno calorico di base per le funzioni corporee di base."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:462
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:416
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:471
msgid "TDEE (Total Daily Energy Expenditure)"
msgstr "TDEE (Dispendio energetico giornaliero totale)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:464
msgid ""
"Your total daily calorie burn including activity. This is the number of "
"calories you need to maintain your current weight."
msgstr ""
"Il consumo totale di calorie giornaliere, inclusa l'attività. Questo è il "
"numero di calorie necessarie per mantenere il peso attuale."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:468
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:287
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:318
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:477
msgid "Calorie Targets"
msgstr "Obiettivi calorici"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:470
msgid ""
"Different calorie goals for weight loss, maintenance, or weight gain. A "
"deficit of 500 calories per day typically results in ~0.5 kg (1 lb) weight "
"loss per week."
msgstr ""
"Obiettivi calorici diversi per perdita di peso, mantenimento o aumento di "
"peso. Un deficit di 500 calorie al giorno si traduce in genere in una "
"perdita di peso di circa 0,5 kg (1 libbra) a settimana."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:476
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Recommended protein, carbohydrate, and fat intake based on your TDEE. "
"Protein is calculated at 1.6g per kg body weight, fat at 25%% of calories, "
"and carbs make up the remainder."
msgstr ""
"Assunzione consigliata di proteine, carboidrati e grassi in base al TDEE. Si"
" calcola che le proteine ​​siano 1,6 g per kg di peso corporeo, i grassi "
"rappresentino il 25%% delle calorie e i carboidrati costituiscano il resto."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:484
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:414
msgid "Weight Management Tips"
msgstr "Suggerimenti per la gestione del peso"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:486
msgid "For Weight Loss:"
msgstr "Per la perdita di peso:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:486
msgid ""
"Create a calorie deficit of 500-1000 calories per day. Focus on whole foods,"
" increase protein intake, and combine diet with regular exercise."
msgstr ""
"Crea un deficit calorico di 500-1000 calorie al giorno. Concentrati sui cibi"
" integrali, aumenta l’apporto proteico e combina la dieta con un regolare "
"esercizio fisico."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:487
msgid "For Weight Maintenance:"
msgstr "Per il mantenimento del peso:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:487
msgid ""
"Eat at your TDEE level. Monitor your weight weekly and adjust calories as "
"needed based on activity changes."
msgstr ""
"Mangia al tuo livello TDEE. Monitora il tuo peso settimanalmente e regola le"
" calorie secondo necessità in base ai cambiamenti dell'attività."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:488
msgid "For Weight Gain:"
msgstr "Per l'aumento di peso:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:488
msgid ""
"Create a calorie surplus of 250-500 calories per day. Focus on nutrient-"
"dense foods and strength training to build muscle rather than fat."
msgstr ""
"Crea un surplus calorico di 250-500 calorie al giorno. Concentrati su cibi "
"ricchi di nutrienti e allenamento per la forza per costruire muscoli "
"piuttosto che grasso."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:500
msgid ""
"BMR calculations are estimates. Individual metabolism can vary based on "
"genetics, muscle mass, hormones, and other factors."
msgstr ""
"I calcoli del BMR sono stime. Il metabolismo individuale può variare in base"
" alla genetica, alla massa muscolare, agli ormoni e ad altri fattori."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:506
msgid ""
"Activity multipliers are approximations. Your actual calorie burn may differ"
" based on exercise intensity and duration."
msgstr ""
"I moltiplicatori di attività sono approssimazioni. Il consumo calorico "
"effettivo può variare in base all'intensità e alla durata dell'esercizio."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:512
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:558
msgid ""
"For best results, track your food intake and weight regularly, and adjust "
"your calorie targets based on your progress."
msgstr ""
"Per ottenere i migliori risultati, monitora regolarmente l'assunzione di "
"cibo e il peso e regola i tuoi obiettivi calorici in base ai tuoi progressi."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:518
msgid ""
"Consult with a healthcare provider or registered dietitian before making "
"significant dietary changes, especially if you have medical conditions."
msgstr ""
"Consulta un operatore sanitario o un dietista registrato prima di apportare "
"modifiche significative alla tua dieta, soprattutto se soffri di patologie."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:687
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:735
msgid "Extreme Loss"
msgstr "Perdita estrema"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:688
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:117
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:736
msgid "Weight Loss"
msgstr "Perdita di peso"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:689
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:737
