msgstr "Sopra la media: ≥ 25%%"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:400
msgid ""
"Body fat percentage is above average. Focus on strength training, cardio, "
