#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/area_calculator.html:360
msgid "What is the Area Calculator?"
msgstr "Cos'è il calcolatore dell'area?"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/area_calculator.html:362
msgid ""
"The Area Calculator is a free tool that calculates the area of various "
"geometric shapes with high precision. It uses advanced mathematical formulas"
" and provides step-by-step solutions to help you understand the calculation "
"process."
msgstr ""
"Il calcolatore di area è uno strumento gratuito che calcola l'area di varie "
"forme geometriche con elevata precisione. Utilizza formule matematiche "
"avanzate e fornisce soluzioni passo passo per aiutarti a comprendere il "
"processo di calcolo."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/area_calculator.html:365
msgid ""
"This calculator supports 13 different geometric shapes including rectangles,"
" circles, triangles, polygons, and more. Each calculation includes detailed "
"results, formulas, and visual representations."
msgstr ""
"Questa calcolatrice supporta 13 diverse forme geometriche tra cui "
"rettangoli, cerchi, triangoli, poligoni e altro. Ogni calcolo include "
"risultati dettagliati, formule e rappresentazioni visive."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/area_calculator.html:373
msgid ""
"Select a shape from the dropdown menu (Rectangle, Circle, Triangle, etc.)"
msgstr ""
"Seleziona una forma dal menu a discesa (Rettangolo, Cerchio, Triangolo, "
"ecc.)"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/area_calculator.html:374
msgid ""
"Choose your preferred unit of measurement (meters, centimeters, inches, "
"etc.)"
msgstr ""
"Scegli l'unità di misura che preferisci (metri, centimetri, pollici, ecc.)"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/area_calculator.html:375
msgid "Enter the required dimensions for your selected shape"
msgstr "Inserisci le dimensioni richieste per la forma selezionata"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/area_calculator.html:376
msgid "Click 'Calculate Area' to get instant results"
msgstr "Fai clic su \"Calcola area\" per ottenere risultati immediati"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/area_calculator.html:377
#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/circle_calculator.html:361
msgid "View detailed results, formulas, and step-by-step solutions"
